          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p>Our Educators</p>",
            "heading_size": "2xl",
            "heading_size_desktop": "2xl",
            "heading_tracking_font": "tracking-0"
          }
        },
        "heading_6fJUQK": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p>Victoria Lynch</p>",
            "heading_size": "lg",
            "heading_size_desktop": "lg",
            "heading_tracking_font": "tracking-0"
          }
        },
        "text_WNk9gG": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>As Managing Director of Remi Cachet, Victoria Lynch has helped provide thousands of stylists with innovative and groundbreaking hair extensions & tools. </p><p>Victoria’s passion for our industry is contagious. Your training will be delivered by one of the UK’s leading Hair Extension experts. </p>",
            "text_size": "base",
            "text_size_desktop": "base"
          }
        },
        "heading_7DhBpE": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<p>Abigail Nicholls</p>",
            "heading_size": "lg",
            "heading_size_desktop": "lg",
            "heading_tracking_font": "tracking-0"
          }
        },
        "text_jHPP8z": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Abigail Nicholls is a Level 3 Educator with over 25 years of experience in hairdressing and has helped deliver education for Remi Cachet Internationally. </p><p>Abigail runs her salon in Exeter, and we are thankful to recognise her as our leading Hair Extension educator. </p><p>If you're ready to evolve your skills, get in touch and secure your space on our exclusive training courses. Remi Cachet can only provide training to those holding an NVQ Level 2 or above, or local equivalent.</p>",
            "text_size": "base",
            "text_size_desktop": "base"
          }
        },
        "button_eKkYwc": {
